Document: Sprite2D
Path: godot/classes/class_sprite2d.rst
Summary: A 2D node that displays a texture.

Sprite2D is a 2D node that displays a texture. It is commonly used for 2D sprites, characters, and other visual elements in a 2D game.

Inherits: Node2D < CanvasItem < Node

This is the base class for 2D nodes that display a texture.
