Document: Sprite2D
Path: godot/classes/class_sprite2d.rst
Summary: Describes the Sprite2D node, which is used to display 2D textures in Godot.

Sprite2D is a node that displays a 2D texture. The texture displayed can be a region from a larger atlas texture, or a frame from a sprite sheet animation.
